overview: Pro Wrestling Guerrilla held their latest event - NINETEEN - on Sunday, July 3, at the Globe Theatre in Los Angeles, California. The event featured the likes of 'Speedball' Mike Bailey, Davey Richards, and Yuka Sakazaki in action and the show was headlined by a PWG World Title match between Daniel Garcia and Konosuke Takeshita.
title: PWG: Nineteen
